#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid "In this module, you can change &kde; default components."
msgstr "V tem modulu lahko spremenite &kde; privzete komponente."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Components are programs that handle basic tasks, like the web browser, "
"terminal emulator, the file manager, the email client, the electronic map, "
"and the dialer. Different &kde; applications sometimes need to invoke a "
"console emulator, send an email, manage files and folders, show the map or "
"dial a number on your phone."
msgstr ""
"Komponente so programi, ki opravljajo osnovna opravila, kot so spletni "
"brskalnik, terminalski emulator, upravitelj datotek, \n"
"odjemalec e-pošte, elektronski zemljevid in klicalnik. Različne &kde; "
"aplikacije morajo včasih priklicati konzolni emulator, poslati e-pošto, "
"upravljati datoteke in mape, prikazati zemljevid ali poklicati številko v "
"telefonu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To do so consistently, these applications always call the same components. "
"Here you can select which programs these components are."
msgstr ""
"Za dosledno delovanje, te aplikacije vedno kličejo iste komponente. Tu lahko "
"izberete, kateri programi so te komponente."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid "The list on the left shows the configurable component types:"
msgstr ""
"Seznam na levi strani prikazuje vrste komponent, ki jih je mogoče "
"konfigurirati:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid "Web Browser"
msgstr "Spletni brskalnik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid "File Manager"
msgstr "Upravitelj datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid "Email Client"
msgstr "Odjemalec e-pošte"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "Terminal Emulator"
msgstr "Terminalski emulator"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Map</para>"
msgstr "<para>Zemljevid</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid "Dialer"
msgstr "Klicalnik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click the combo box of the component you want to configure. In the list, "
"select your favorite web browser, file manager, email client, terminal "
"emulator, map, and dialer. Choose <guimenuitem>Other...</guimenuitem> to "
"open the <guilabel>Choose Application</guilabel> dialog and select your "
"application manually."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite izbirno okno komponente, ki jo želite konfigurirati. Na seznamu "
"izberite najljubši spletni brskalnik, upravitelja datotek, odjemalca e-"
"pošte, emulator terminala, zemljevid in klicalnik. Izberite "
"<guimenuitem>Other. . . </guimenuitem>, da odprete pogovorno okno "
"<guilabel>Choose Application</guilabel> in ročno izberete aplikacijo."
